                                                    <h2 class="text-center">How Does It Work</h2>
                                                    <div class="home-steps container-12">

                                                        <div class="grid-6 text-center mob_visible"><img title="Get notification for incoming mail" src="https://www.postscanmail.com/sites/default/files/step1_graphic.png" alt="How Virtual Mail Works?" width="214" height="125"></div>
                                                        <div class="grid-6">
                                                            <h3 class="hel_bld_cd">Your Mail Arrives..</h3>
                                                            <p>Once you create an account at PostScan Mail, our staff takes action. You receive a <a href="https://www.postscanmail.com/services/virtual-address/po-box-with-street-address">U.S. street address</a> at which to receive your mail at a PostScan Mail facility.</p>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <div class="grid-6 text-center mob_hidden"><img title="Online Mailbox Rental" src="https://www.postscanmail.com/sites/default/files/step1_graphic.png" alt="Virtual Mailing Address" width="214" height="125"><p> </p>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <div class="clearboth"><p></p></div>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <div class="home-steps container-12 clearboth midrow">
                                                        <div class="grid-6 text-center"><img title="Get notification for incoming mail" src="https://www.postscanmail.com/sites/default/files/step2_graphic.png" alt="How Virtual Mail Works?" width="214" height="125"></div>
                                                        <div class="grid-6">
                                                            <h3 class="hel_bld_cd">Get a Notification..</h3>
                                                            <p>When mail arrives addressed to your unique address at the facility, we notify you of its arrival, scan the front of the item, and make the image available to you online for review.</p>
                                                        </div>

                                                        <div class="clearboth"><p></p></div>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <div class="home-steps container-12 clearfix">

                                                        <div class="grid-6 text-center mob_visible"><img title="Get notification for incoming mail" src="https://www.postscanmail.com/sites/default/files/step3_graphic.png" alt="How Virtual Mail Works?" width="214" height="125"></div>
                                                        <div class="grid-6 clearfix">
                                                            <h3 class="hel_bld_cd">Determine what's next..</h3>
                                                            <p>You simply review the image, and decide how you want the mail piece handled. You can either Open &amp; <a href="https://www.postscanmail.com/services/mail/scanning">Scan</a>, Recycle, Shred, or <a href="https://www.postscanmail.com/services/mail/forwarding">Forward</a> the mail piece. You can also decide to store it.</p>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <div class="grid-6 clearfix text-center mob_hidden"><img title="virtual mailbox" src="https://www.postscanmail.com/sites/default/files/step3_graphic.png" alt="virtual mail box" width="214" height="125">
